      <title>斯里兰卡官方债权人签署 59 亿美元债务重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/sri-lanka-official-creditors-agree-to-restructure-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡与印度和巴黎俱乐部等官方债权人委员会达成原则协议，重组约 59 亿美元的债务，这是该国努力从前所未有的经济危机中复苏的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/sri-lanka-official-creditors-agree-to-restructure-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 09:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议员称德国面临 240 亿欧元预算缺口的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/germany-may-have-24-billion-budget-hole-in-2024-lawmaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨执政联盟的一位高级议员表示，德国 2024 年预算可能存在高达 240 亿欧元（合 264 亿美元）的缺口，但具体数字仍悬而未决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/germany-may-have-24-billion-budget-hole-in-2024-lawmaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 09:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
